OOC: I've been an expert on Dinosaurs since Nursery School, so id have to 
agree with Soulstice.  Raptors were only about 3 feet tall.

:::The Protectrons/Torca/Ratchet/Sideswipe/Sky Lynx/Orion/Wheeljack:::

Torca: Yes, im Torca, and Iron Raptor is still leader.  Deemos?  If your 
talking about the cowardly leader of the Chosen Mafia, hes still alive.
::All of my Maximals hear the transmission::
Hardhead: Damn, whats with all the battles?
Chromedome: Shut up Hardhead, we're Maximals now, and that means we will help 
them when they are in need.
Sideswipe: You know, hes right.
Ratchet: Yeah, the war has been escalating recently...
::Ratchet fuels some shuttles, with them teaming up in groups of three.  
Torca, Orion, and Highbrow get in to one, Ratchet, Sideswipe, and Sky Lynx 
get into another, and Chromedome, Hardhead, and Brainstorm get into the last 
one and they get ready to take off::
~~~~~
::Wheeljack smiled at Composer's enthusiasm::
Wheeljack: Alrighty then!  Composer, follow me.
::He heads to the controls of the sheilds and everything else and waits for 
Composer::

--part1_fe.209c163.27b35e8c_boundary
